IDENTIFICATION DIVISION.
PROGRAM-ID. DEPOSIT.

DATA DIVISION.
WORKING-STORAGE SECTION.
01 WS-CMDLINE     PIC X(100).
01 WS-BAL-TEXT    PIC X(30).
01 WS-AMT-TEXT    PIC X(30).
01 WS-BALANCE     PIC S9(13)V99.
01 WS-AMOUNT      PIC S9(13)V99.

PROCEDURE DIVISION.
    ACCEPT WS-CMDLINE FROM COMMAND-LINE

    UNSTRING WS-CMDLINE DELIMITED BY SPACE
        INTO WS-BAL-TEXT WS-AMT-TEXT

    MOVE FUNCTION NUMVAL(WS-BAL-TEXT) TO WS-BALANCE
    MOVE FUNCTION NUMVAL(WS-AMT-TEXT) TO WS-AMOUNT

    IF WS-AMT-TEXT = SPACES OR WS-BAL-TEXT = SPACES
        DISPLAY "INVALID"
        STOP RUN
    END-IF

    IF WS-AMOUNT <= 0
        DISPLAY "INVALID"
        STOP RUN
    END-IF

    ADD WS-AMOUNT TO WS-BALANCE
    DISPLAY WS-BALANCE
    STOP RUN.


